38 //
39 // Class for relative state computed between PositionVelocity and
40 // PlanarDubins3D.
41 //
42 // NOTE! Because this is a relative state, we do NOT support
43 // sampling or configuration space conversions.
44 //
46 
47 #ifndef FASTRACK_STATE_POSITION_VELOCITY_REL_PLANAR_DUBINS_3D_H
48 #define FASTRACK_STATE_POSITION_VELOCITY_REL_PLANAR_DUBINS_3D_H
49 
50 #include <fastrack/state/relative_state.h>
51 #include <fastrack/state/position_velocity.h>
52 #include <fastrack/state/planar_dubins_3d.h>
53 
54 namespace fastrack {
55 namespace state {
56 
57 class PositionVelocityRelPlanarDubins3D
58  : public RelativeState<PositionVelocity, PlanarDubins3D> {
59 public:
60  ~PositionVelocityRelPlanarDubins3D() {}
61 
62  // NOTE! We do NOT provide a default constructor. Objects from this
63  // class SHOULD be initialized from the two corresponding states.
64  explicit PositionVelocityRelPlanarDubins3D(const PositionVelocity &tracker_x,
65  const PlanarDubins3D &planner_x)
66  : distance_(std::hypot(tracker_x.X() - planner_x.X(),
67  tracker_x.Y() - planner_x.Y())),
68  bearing_(std::atan2(tracker_x.Y() - planner_x.Y(),
69  tracker_x.X() - planner_x.X())),
70  tangent_velocity_(std::cos(planner_x.Theta()) * tracker_x.Vx() +
71  std::sin(planner_x.Theta()) * planner_x.Vy()),
72  normal_velocity_(-std::sin(planner_x.Theta()) * tracker_x.Vx() +
73  std::cos(planner_x.Theta()) * planner_x.Vy()) {}
74 
75  // Construct directly.
76  explicit PositionVelocityRelPlanarDubins3D(double distance, double bearing,
77  double tangent_v, double normal_v)
78  : distance_(distance), bearing_(bearing), tangent_velocity_(tangent_v),
79  normal_velocity_(normal_v) {}
80 
81  // Dimension of the state space.
82  static constexpr size_t StateDimension() { return 4; }
83 
84  // Accessors.
85  inline double Distance() const { return distance_; }
86  inline double Bearing() const { return bearing_; }
87  inline double TangentVelocity() const { return tangent_velocity_; }
88  inline double NormalVelocity() const { return normal_velocity_; }
89 
90 private:
91  // Relative (x, y) distance.
92  const double distance_;
93 
94  // Relative bearing in the (x, y) plane.
95  const double bearing_;
96 
97  // PositionVelocity's relative velocity along PlanarDubins3D's heading.
98  // (in Frenet frame).
99  const double tangent_velocity_;
100 
101  // PositionVelocity's relative velocity normal to PlanarDubins3D's heading.
102  // (in Frenet frame).
103  const double normal_velocity_;
104 }; //\class PositionVelocityRelPlanarDubins3D
105

107 } // namespace fastrack
